entry.title: Welcome to Orangy's new docs!
entry.summary: Hey there, and welcome to Orangy's new docs website!
entry.content:
Hey there, and welcome to Orangy's new docs website! This website currently includes the Documentation and Changelog categories, but a few more things may be added in the near future!

We will be adding some info about the new bot updates in here, along with a few posts about Orangy v2 (that's going to be released pretty soon üëÄ). Make sure to join Orangy's official Discord server to stay updated! üçä

Also thank you for (probably) clicking on "Read More" :)
